Detailed Description

Different calculation methods for orientation error.

As I can only pass strings through MoveIt planning requests it does not really work with enums of integral type. Therefore I came up with this akward hack, which I think is still better than magic with implicit casting. This hack should result in almost the same syntax.

Is there name collision danger with QUATERNION?
